        {
            "review_id": "225739517",
            "steam_id": "76561198334300945",
            "playtime_minutes": 2901,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 2,
            "weighted_score": 0.5438839197158813,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "!00% bias opinion on this game-\r\n\r\nI personally enjoy this game so much and might be hands down one of the best \"party\" games to play with your friends. \r\n\r\nGames can last decently long, with that being said, you can just edit the settings to make the game's pace faster and I would recommend you do that. The basic minigames can be super fun but some kinda do really suck so I would figure out which ones you don't like and just deselect them. As well as the maps, some are pretty cool but not very interactive most of the time. BUT some cool people decided to make tons of modded maps and modded minigames which I would HIGHLY recommend that you add. \r\n\r\nAnyways... for the most part this game has a good mix of RNG and skill but it is HEAVLY RNG sided which makes it all the more fun and chaotic and wouldn't change it for a second lol...\r\n\r\nHope this helps!\r\n\r\nAboslutely worth the price and would buy it 10x's over again"
        },
        {
            "review_id": "225714974",
            "steam_id": "76561198331590586",
            "playtime_minutes": 5142,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 2,
            "weighted_score": 0.5243030786514282,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Very much a more violent mario party. I have bought this game for a few of my friends and they all love it. its a great game to play with friends if you like messing with your friends and making them rage. If you like mario party you will more than likely like this game. \n\n\n\n♥♥♥♥ BOT JACK"
        },
